            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01AJbxevS5g4ECHZqs4F8QSy\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"As expected, the `NonExistent.tsx` file doesn't exist. The errors are:\\n\\n1. **Syntax Error**: The component has two root elements without a wrapper (lines 5-8)\\n2. **Import Error**: Importing a component that doesn't exist (line 1)\\n\\nLet me fix the IndexPage.tsx file by removing the non-existent component and fixing the JSX structure:\"},{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_014Beb4zGsRM6RhwKEREbWo7\",\"name\":\"edit_file\",\"input\":{\"file_path\":\"/src/pages/IndexPage.tsx\",\"old_string\":\"import { NonExistentComponent } from \\\"../components/NonExistent.tsx\\\";\\n\\nexport const IndexPage = () => {\\n  return (\\n      <NonExistentComponent />\\n    <div className=\\\"min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-background\\\">\\n      <h1 className=\\\"text-4xl font-bold text-foreground\\\">Hello World</h1>\\n    </div>\\n  );\\n};\",\"new_string\":\"export const IndexPage = () => {\\n  return (\\n    <div className=\\\"min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-background\\\">\\n      <h1 className=\\\"text-4xl font-bold text-foreground\\\">Hello World</h1>\\n    </div>\\n  );\\n};\",\"replace_all\":false}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":5,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":160,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":8433,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":160,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":376,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
